Package: quickie
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libcap-ng0, libpython3.7
Description: Python runtime wrapper which set capabilities to bind root ports
 This small Python runtime wrapper automatically set capabilities to bind
 IP ports under 1024. Therefore you don't need to be root to run Python
 module listening on these protected ports.
